column1: Cognitive Scientist with expertise in machine learning and data analysis, proficient in Python and SQL. Skilled in developing applications and extracting insights through data mining. Successfully completed projects, including building a Django web app, automating an eCommerce store, and creating a data-driven sales dashboard to enhance net sales while reducing costs. Passionate about transforming information into actionable outcomes. Seeking opportunities in tech or finance to drive net profit, optimize resource utilization, and implement customer feedback.
